headline: How AI Is Impacting Productivity at JPM, BAC, C & Others
summary: AI is driving productivity gains at JPMorgan, Citigroup, Bank of America, WFC and PNC, reshaping workflows, budgets, and potentially, bank staffing.

headline: Wells Fargo sees digital boost from branch refurbishments
summary: The bank plans to renovate branches in Los Angeles, San Francisco and Atlanta in 2026, the lender’s head of branch systems and transformation said.
